traits.description: You face danger without flinching, your courage bolstering your mental resilience against fear and intimidation.

You have an insatiable desire to learn and discover new things, your constant study making you more academically knowledgeable.
You value truth and speak it even when it's difficult, your transparent nature making you more persuasive when your sincerity shines through.
Once you give your word or friendship, you keep it no matter the cost, your unwavering dedication strengthening your mental fortitude.
You see the bright side of situations and believe things will work out, your positive demeanor naturally attracting others to your company.
You have strong self-control and stick to routines and commitments, your mental training enhancing your ability to maintain concentration.
You have a sharp mind and quick tongue, often lightening moods with humor and clever verbal expressions.

You act on instinct and emotion, rarely thinking through consequences, your quick reflexes and coordination offset by poor logical reasoning.

You are grounded and down to earth, never boasting about your accomplishments despite your capabilities, your modesty making you more likeable.
